isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-06/ty-article/.premium/police-detain-palestinian-photographer-who-was-attacked-by-jewish-youths-at-jlem-march/0000018f-eec9-de64-a98f-eeffbd320000</guid></item><item><title>以色列在六日战争中的神话般的胜利如何成为犹太极右翼的仇恨盛宴</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-06-06/ty-article/.premium/how-israels-mythic-victory-in-the-six-day-war-became-a-jewish-far-right-hate-fest/0000018f-ee29-dff6-a9df-efbbafb80000</link><description>周三，右翼以色列人庆祝六日战争中耶路撒冷的统一，以表达反阿拉伯仇恨。其丑陋的神话可能会让更多的以色列人看到军事力量的影响</description><pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 18:37:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-06-06/ty-article/.premium/how-israels-mythic-victory-in-the-six-day-war-became-a-jewish-far-right-hate-fest/0000018f-ee29-dff6-a9df-efbbafb80000</guid></item><item><title>以色列抗议者接到警方电话，要求他在骄傲集会游行中排除政治因素</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-06/ty-article/.premium/israeli-protester-gets-police-call-telling-him-to-bar-politics-from-march-to-pride-rally/0000018f-ee6a-d5c6-a1cf-fe7e64a30000</link><description>一名警官告诉“粉红阵线”联合创始人亚尼夫·西格尔，要确保该组织参加集会而不是通常的骄傲游行的游行中不会有“政治因素”</description><pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 18:10:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-06/ty-article/.premium/israeli-protester-gets-police-call-telling-him-to-bar-politics-from-march-to-pride-rally/0000018f-ee6a-d5c6-a1cf-fe7e64a30000</guid></item><item><title>解释：“沙希德”或“烈士”对巴勒斯坦人和以色列人意味着什么</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-06/ty-article/.premium/explained-what-shahid-or-martyr-means-for-palestinians-and-israelis/0000018f-e351-d1da-adaf-f7df71ae0000</link><description>自 20 世纪 90 年代巴勒斯坦自杀式爆炸事件以来，对于以色列境内讲希伯来语的人来说，“沙希德”一词一直是“恐怖分子”的代名词。现在这个词从半岛电视台到美国校园都在使用，Facebook 上禁止使用该词，并被以色列执法部门视为煽动行为，那么“烈士”对于以色列、加沙和约旦河西岸讲阿拉伯语的人来说到底意味着什么？</description><pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 17:11:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-06/ty-article/.premium/explained-what-shahid-or-martyr-means-for-palestinians-and-israelis/0000018f-e351-d1da-adaf-f7df71ae0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第 244 天：以色列将建立伤员离开加沙系统</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-06-06/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-244-israel-to-set-up-system-for-wounded-people-to-leave-gaza/0000018f-ee78-d660-af9f-effe42820000</link><description>以色列北部指挥部负责人表示，以色列国防军已完成对真主党袭击的准备工作。 ■ 美国和其他 16 个国家呼吁以色列、哈马斯“做出一切必要的最终妥协”，以确保停战。进出加沙的病人 ■ 西班牙将加入南非国际法院的案件，指控以色列在加沙实施种族灭绝 ■ 战争进入 244 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 16:58:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-06-06/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-244-israel-to-set-up-system-for-wounded-people-to-leave-gaza/0000018f-ee78-d660-af9f-effe42820000</guid></item><item><title>认识自 1976 年以来首位代表以色列参加奥运会的阿拉伯裔以色列运动员</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-06/ty-article/.premium/meet-the-first-palestinian-athlete-to-represent-israel-at-the-olympics-since-1976/0000018f-edb5-d36e-abcf-fdf5c3d90000</link><description>即将前往巴黎的以色列游泳运动员亚当·马拉纳 (Adam Mara&amp;#39;ana) 表示：“我自己都感到惊讶，也很高兴”</description><pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 15:59:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-06/ty-article/.premium/meet-the-first-palestinian-athlete-to-represent-israel-at-the-olympics-since-1976/0000018f-edb5-d36e-abcf-fdf5c3d90000</guid></item><item><title>特拉维夫的骄傲活动展示了一个因战争而发生巨大变化的酷儿社区</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-06-06/ty-article/.premium/tel-avivs-pride-events-present-a-queer-community-dramatically-changed-by-war/0000018f-edd0-d75d-a18f-efd224fe0000</link><description>同样在本周，Artport 艺术中心的年度艺术书展回归； 10 月 7 日，英雄诺姆·蒂邦 (Noam Tibon) 将成为 Fauda 创作者制作的电影的主题；死于加沙的人质查姆·佩里 (Chaim Peri) 创作的儿童读物现已出版</description><pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 15:46:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-06-06/ty-article/.premium/tel-avivs-pride-events-present-a-queer-community-dramatically-changed-by-war/0000018f-edd0-d75d-a18f-efd224fe0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列主要抗议团体针对右翼诽谤提起诽谤诉讼</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-06/ty-article/.premium/leading-israeli-protest-group-files-defamation-suits-against-right-wing-slander/0000018f-ed82-d36e-abcf-fdc6e8f60000</link><description>自哈马斯 10 月 7 日发动袭击以来的几个月里，极右翼专家经常指责以色列军队预备役组织“武装兄弟姐妹”，声称他们在反对总理内塔尼亚胡司法改革的抗议活动中呼吁拒绝服兵役，这激励了哈马斯打击以色列</description><pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 15:12:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-06/ty-article/.premium/leading-israeli-protest-group-files-defamation-suits-against-right-wing-slander/0000018f-ed82-d36e-abcf-fdc6e8f60000</guid></item><item><title>TikTok 令以色列担忧。与此同时，22 名部长迷上了这款应用</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/tech-news/2024-06-06/ty-article/.premium/israel-is-worried-about-tiktok-meanwhile-22-of-its-ministers-are-hooked-on-the-app/0000018f-ed72-d9ce-a5cf-ffffd4610000</link><description>“TikTok 对国家安全构成战略威胁”：以色列议会的一次讨论暴露了以色列政府未能解决日益严重的操纵社交平台的问题，该平台被 380 万以色列人使用，其中包括国家安全部长</description><pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 13:42:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/tech-news/2024-06-06/ty-article/.premium/israel-is-worried-about-tiktok-meanwhile-22-of-its-ministers-are-hooked-on-the-app/0000018f-ed72-d9ce-a5cf-ffffd4610000</guid></item><item><title>以色列对加沙近东救济工程处学校的袭击造成数十人死亡；以色列国防军：哈马斯利用建筑物作为基地</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-06/ty-article/.premium/dozens-killed-in-israeli-strike-on-unrwa-school-in-gaza-idf-hamas-used-building-as-base/0000018f-ed20-dba5-afdf-ffb2a6480000</link><description>虽然以色列军方表示，近东救济工程处在努塞拉特的学校关押着参加 10 月 7 日的哈马斯和伊斯兰圣战恐怖分子精英，但哈马斯表示，该学校关押着流离失所的加沙人，并不是军事大院。</description><pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 11:32:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-06/ty-article/.premium/dozens-killed-in-israeli-strike-on-unrwa-school-in-gaza-idf-hamas-used-building-as-base/0000018f-ed20-dba5-afdf-ffb2a6480000</guid></item><item><title>以色列前最高法院院长因个人原因辞去国际法院职务</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-06/ty-article/.premium/former-israeli-supreme-court-president-resigns-from-icj-citing-personal-reasons/0000018f-ecad-dba5-afdf-febfb2e80000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡总理现在必须任命大屠杀幸存者阿哈龙·巴拉克的继任者，巴拉克认为，只要以色列履行《种族灭绝公约》规定的义务，以色列就没有义务停止加沙南部的战斗</description><pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 10:48:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-06/ty-article/.premium/former-israeli-supreme-court-president-resigns-from-icj-citing-personal-reasons/0000018f-ecad-dba5-afdf-febfb2e80000</guid></item><item><title>当以色列人发现自己被困在贝鲁特机场时</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/travel/2024-06-06/ty-article-magazine/.premium/when-israelis-find-themselves-stranded-at-beiruts-airport/0000018f-e7b6-d11f-a5cf-e7bfac3b0000</link><description>以色列军队一直在干扰 GPS 服务，以迷惑敌人。重新找回失去的方向感的机会</description><pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 10:32:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/travel/2024-06-06/ty-article-magazine/.premium/when-israelis-find-themselves-stranded-at-beiruts-airport/0000018f-e7b6-d11f-a5cf-e7bfac3b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列士兵在黎巴嫩边境附近真主党无人机袭击中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-06/ty-article/israeli-soldier-killed-in-hezbollah-drone-attack-near-lebanon-border/0000018f-ecef-dcb4-a38f-fdefb19d0000</link><description>参谋军士。 (res.) 拉斐尔·考德斯 (Refael Kauders) 在真主党无人机袭击以色列北部边境德鲁兹城镇胡尔菲什 (Hurfeish) 附近的军事阵地时身亡</description><pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 10:07:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-06/ty-article/israeli-soldier-killed-in-hezbollah-drone-attack-near-lebanon-border/0000018f-ecef-dcb4-a38f-fdefb19d0000</guid></item><item><title>恐怖分子计划袭击以色列领土开火，突破加沙缓冲区，以色列国防军士兵被杀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-06/ty-article/.premium/terrorists-planning-raid-on-israeli-soil-breach-buffer-zone-with-gaza-fire-at-idf-forces/0000018f-ec7f-dcb4-a38f-fd7f40ad0000</link><description>至少三名恐怖分子闯入以色列控制的加沙边境缓冲区，其装备表明他们计划袭击以色列军事基地或边境社区，被以色列军队击毙</description><pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 08:45:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-06/ty-article/.premium/terrorists-planning-raid-on-israeli-soil-breach-buffer-zone-with-gaza-fire-at-idf-forces/0000018f-ec7f-dcb4-a38f-fd7f40ad0000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯声称以色列和美国停火提议存在差异，要求调解员澄清</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-06/ty-article/.premium/hamas-claims-disparity-between-israeli-and-u-s-cease-fire-deals-requests-clarification/0000018f-ec5c-da58-a1ef-fcde15270000</link><description>哈马斯在发给巴勒斯坦各派别的一份备忘录中表示，在与调解人会谈后，很明显以色列只对实施该提案的第一阶段感兴趣，并且避免承诺从加沙完全撤军</description><pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 07:46:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-06/ty-article/.premium/hamas-claims-disparity-between-israeli-and-u-s-cease-fire-deals-requests-clarification/0000018f-ec5c-da58-a1ef-fcde15270000</guid></item><item><title>过去 16 年里我看过每一次耶路撒冷旗帜游行。这个是最丑的</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-06/ty-article/.premium/if-jerusalem-day-is-an-accurate-thermometer-of-israeli-society-the-diagnosis-is-terminal/0000018f-eab4-d463-a19f-ffbd44ad0000</link><description>前几年，官员们做出了一些努力来平息事态。今年，年轻人似乎可以随意呼喊种族主义口号、骚乱以及攻击他们遇到的任何人。</description><pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 03:09:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-06/ty-article/.premium/if-jerusalem-day-is-an-accurate-thermometer-of-israeli-society-the-diagnosis-is-terminal/0000018f-eab4-d463-a19f-ffbd44ad0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列和真主党之间的边缘政策可能将双方推向边缘</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-06/ty-article/.premium/brinkmanship-between-israel-and-hezbollah-could-push-both-sides-over-the-edge/0000018f-e9f1-dc46-a5bf-f9f58e310000</link><description>以色列总参谋部努力向真主党展示全面战争将带来的代价。对黎巴嫩的破坏将是巨大的，但对以色列北部和中部城市可能造成的破坏不同于哈马斯所经历的任何破坏</description><pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 03:00:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-06/ty-article/.premium/brinkmanship-between-israel-and-hezbollah-could-push-both-sides-over-the-edge/0000018f-e9f1-dc46-a5bf-f9f58e310000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军称，闯入加沙缓冲区的恐怖分子从以色列边境附近的隧道中出现</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-06/ty-article-live/israel-terrorists-who-took-part-in-october-7-massacre-killed-in-strike-on-hamas-compound/0000018f-eb4c-d4cf-abcf-ef4d922b0000</link><description>以色列国防军宣布一名在加沙战斗中丧生的士兵死亡 ■ 加沙官员称，以色列袭击努塞拉特学校造成 40 人死亡 ■ 由于财务状况，巴勒斯坦权力机构将向其员工支付一半工资 ■ 以色列国防军宣布一名在黎巴嫩边境附近的无人机袭击中受伤的士兵死亡 ■ 三人恐怖分子在试图从加沙南部进入以色列时被杀</description><pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 02:18:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-06/ty-article-live/israel-terrorists-who-took-part-in-october-7-massacre-killed-in-strike-on-hamas-compound/0000018f-eb4c-d4cf-abcf-ef4d922b0000</guid></item></channel></rss>